jexxus.common
Class ByteBuffer

java.lang.Object
  jexxus.common.ByteBuffer

public class ByteBuffer
extends java.lang.Object

Used for storing many forms of data into a single array of bytes. This is useful for serializing objects to send them over the network or save them as a file.

Author:
Jason
